text: After seeing many injustice inside and outside of the pitch, referee appointments&decisions during the games etc, it appears to many of us that we need to sort out our issues within first before competing for the European competitions again.Just like England once asked and did so

author: Görkem K.
text:
Once is a mistake, twice may be a coincidence, but three is a pattern.

This season in Turkish Super League, so many games’ outcomes were directly affected by the decisions of the appointed referees.

Our trust for the sincerity of TFF is shaken.

#UEFADoNotRegisterSuperLeague
